description:
On this episode of ANN International: Annual Council 2023 takes a look at the proposed 2025-2030 “I Will Go” strategic plan for the World Church.

Adventists in the Dominican Republic celebrate 25 years of gospel growth in the region.

An AdventHealth mission trip provides hundreds of families with free health care services in Ecuador. 

Also, thousands of young Adventists gather in Panama for a three-day youth congress and are inspired to “jumpstart” a life with Jesus.

Watch as ANN highlights these stories and reports on other news from around the world. For details on these top stories and more, go to adventist.news.

ANN is the official news channel of the Seventh-day Adventist Church.
